SUMMARY:Question Everything Trivia hosted by QE Trivia @ Tha Phae Tavern
DESCRIPTION:Check out Tha Phae Tavern for a one of a kind trivia experience! \nWHAT TO EXPECT \nYour hostQE owner\, and comedian Ari Issac and the QE Team bring the sass and laughs! \nGames \n\n10 trivia categories testing you on pop culture’s best and brightest celebs\, tv\, movies\, music\, and so much more!\nInteractive games mixed throughout testing your agility and wit for BONUS points!\n\nWHO SHOULD ATTEND \nThink trivia isn’t your thing? Perfect – this is exactly for you. \nAt Question Everything Trivia\, we flip the script on your average game night. Forget boring\, brain-busting questions and awkward silences – this is trivia reimagined. Expect laughs\, sass\, and pop-culture madness that keeps everyone engaged\, whether you know the answers or not. \nWe’re inclusive\, welcoming\, and all about good vibes. \nPRIZES \nPrizes change each week based on sponsors! But they are litty. Here’s what you can generally expect – the host will speak to the exact prizes on the day and the patterns they correspond to 🙂 \n\nGRETA 1 Hour Unlimited Play Cards\n1 Hour Private Karaoke Room Experience\n$25 E Gift Card for Tha Phae Tavern\nTha Phae Tavern Merch 🎶\n\n* Additional prizes change on a week-to-week basis\, and are dependent on weekly sponsors and attendance. \nVENUE & TICKET RULES \nPlease arrive as close to 5:45 as possible to be seated so that the game can start promptly at 6PM \n\nOnce tickets are sold out\, please join waitlist to be the first to know if someone releases their spot last minute.\n$25 Minimum Spend / Person. This is just a couple drinks and food so it shouldn’t be hard to reach\, and helps the bar continue to provide these nights and epic prizes!
URL:https://nowtoronto.com/event/question-everything-trivia-hosted-by-qe-trivia-tha-phae-tavern-4/
LOCATION:Tha Phae Tavern\, 221 Richmond St W\, Toronto\, ON M5V 1W4\, Canada\, Old Toronto\, Toronto\, Ontario\, M5V 1W4
CATEGORIES:Games & Trivia
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://nowtoronto.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/question-everything-trivia-hosted-by-qe-trivia-tha-phae-tavern.png
END:VEVENT
