SUMMARY:Euchre Night at Hugs & Sarcasm
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a night of fun. Euchre Night every Tuesday starting at 7pm  \nBook your spot now\, got a team – great\, flying solo we will pair you up with someone. Spots are limited. \nBeginner? Come a little earlier and we will give you the crash course. \nOur awesome host will be running the show while the Hugs crew keep the drinks flowing. \nFree to play
